яция по числу лет работы"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"collapsed":true,"id":"YGsWlrZtDYPs","outputId":"ddd65ca1-e9b3-4c94-dac4-ec9cf9efeabf","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1779690755545,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":5259,"user":{"displayName":"ИЛЬДОРАДО","userId":"07990994668907174693"}}},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Автокорреляция выгорания (лаг = 1 год): -0.02\n","Автокорреляция продуктивности (лаг = 1 год): 0.99\n"]},{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 1400x500 with 2 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}],"source":["import statsmodels.api as sm\n","\n","\n","# Получаем среднее выгорание и продуктивность для каждого года стажа\n","agg_trends = df.groupby('experience_years')[['burnout_risk_score', 'productivity_score']].mean().reset_index()\n","agg_trends = agg_trends.sort_values('experience_years')\n","\n","# лаг = 1 год\n","autocorr_burnout = agg_trends['burnout_risk_score'].autocorr(lag=1)\n","autocorr_productivity = agg_trends['productivity_score'].autocorr(lag=1)\n","\n","print(f\"Автокорреляция выгорания (лаг = 1 год): {autocorr_burnout:.2f}\")\n","print(f\"Автокорреляция продуктивности (лаг = 1 год): {autocorr_productivity:.2f}\")\n","\n","# Визуализируем\n","fig, (ax1, ax2) = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(14, 5))\n","max_lags = min(10, len(agg_trends) - 2) # Ограничение на количество лагов\n","\n","# График для выгорания\n","sm.graphics.tsa.plot_acf(agg_trends['burnout_risk_score'], lags=max_lags, ax=ax1)\n","ax1.set_title('Автокорреляция: Выгорание по годам стажа')\n","ax1.set_xlabel('Лаг (в годах)')\n","ax1.set_ylabel('Коэффициент автокорреляции')\n","\n","# График для продуктивности\n","sm.graphics.tsa.plot_acf(agg_trends['productivity_score'], lags=max_lags, ax=ax2)\n","ax2.set_title('Автокорреляция: Продуктивность по годам стажа')\n","ax2.set_xlabel('Лаг (в годах)')\n","ax2.set_ylabel('Коэффициент автокорреляции')\n","\n","plt.tight_layout()\n","plt.show()"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"M8lh6GFTDYPs"},"source":["**Выводы**\n","* Автокорреляция выгорания близка к 0. Автокорреляция же продуктивности близка к 1.\n","* Это значит, что люди, продуктивно работавшие в прошлый год, будут так же хорошо работать в текущий. С выгоранием не так: человек, спокойно работавший в прошлый год, может выгореть в текущем, и наоборот"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"R0feSVNDe5Kj"},"source":["# кластеризация"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"SF2BTP_nlaFe","outputId":"d3487c9e-87c0-475d-9bda-1aaa1cc5f457","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1779690756475,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":927,"user":{"displayName":"ИЛЬДОРАДО","userId":"07990994668907174693"}}},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["\u001b[2mUsing Python 3.12.13 environment at: /usr\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[2mChecked \u001b[1m1 package\u001b[0m \u001b[2min 367ms\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\n"]}],"source":["!uv pip install umap-learn"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"id":"4-h4Z5kFe9r5"},"outputs":[],"source":["import pandas as pd\n","import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n","import seaborn as sns\n","from sklearn.cluster import KMeans\n","from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler\n","from sklearn.metrics import silhouette_score\n","import umap"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"id":"w4C4g3vqfCIv"},"outputs":[],"source":["df = pd.read_csv(file1_path)\n","targets_df = pd.read_csv(file2_path)\n","df = pd.merge(df, targets_df, on='Employee_ID', how='inner')"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"id":"DG91cBwnlpWO"},"outputs":[],"source":["roles = ['Analyst', 'Designer', 'Developer', 'Manager', 'Marketer', 'Writer']"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"id":"8vZlsBT_lq47"},"outputs":[],"source":["df_clusters = {role: {'df' : df[df['job_rol